skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hey daryl
des: This skill is based off two funny charters named Jim Bob and Daryl. Once the user invokes the skill, they will be able to say "Hey Daryl" and get the normal Daryl "Newt Dude", but if a user say "Hey Jim Bob" the response will be "My last hook just went viral". A user can also request help to get the commands or stop/cancel to get out of the skill.
